%2Fv1%2Fbookcenter%2Fcover%2F1%2F3596634%2F3596634_2fa487831390456c8bbabf1e009363ce.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=\"https://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/img-bk.png\"' alt=\"择天记\" class=\"cover\"/> <div class=\"right\"> <h4 class=\"name\"> <a href=\"/book/613843fb4f3a0f02f9568cc5\" target=\"_blank\">择天记</a> </h4> <p class=\"author\"> <span>猫腻</span> <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"cat\">玄幻</span> </p> <p class=\"desc\">命里有时终须有，命里无时要强求。\n\n这是一个长生果的故事。</p> <p class=\"popularity\">  <span class=\"c-red\">2.72万</span>人气  <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"c-red\">71.25%</span>读者留存 </p> </div> <a href=\"/book/613843fb4f3a0f02f9568cc5/1.html\" class=\"btn-read\" target=\"_blank\">开始阅读</a> </div>  <div data-href=\"/book/508a2c7ef5cf27d11500000b\" class=\"book\"> <img src=\"http://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/agent/http%3A%2F%2Fimg.1391.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fbookcenter%2Fcover%2F1%2F685418%2F685418_2491b56f37ae4c4aae27463dd70b2e25.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=\"https://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/img-bk.png\"' alt=\"混沌剑神\" class=\"cover\"/> <div class=\"right\"> <h4 class=\"name\"> <a href=\"/book/508a2c7ef5cf27d11500000b\" target=\"_blank\">混沌剑神</a> </h4> <p class=\"author\"> <span>心星逍遥</span> <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"cat\">玄幻</span> </p> <p class=\"desc\">傲视群雄，俯瞰众生，成就一代完美逍遥剑神！剑尘，他是江湖公认的第一高手，一手快剑出神入化，所向披靡！却意外重生异世，于是他修圣力、练剑意，领悟全新绝技杀敌千里之外，且看他如何搅动乾坤，登顶异界！</p> <p class=\"popularity\">  <span class=\"c-red\">2.99万</span>人气  <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"c-red\">87.01%</span>读者留存 </p> </div> <a href=\"/book/508a2c7ef5cf27d11500000b/1.html\" class=\"btn-read\" target=\"_blank\">开始阅读</a> </div>  <div data-href=\"/book/620a32b99aad6e54aaa27b1d\" class=\"book\"> <img src=\"http://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/agent/http%3A%2F%2Fimg.1391.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fbookcenter%2Fcover%2F1%2F3611093%2F3611093_06fc8f70bd1a4389bd241b91f0f77e8b.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=\"https://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/img-bk.png\"' alt=\"九星霸体诀（又名：玄天霸体录）\" class=\"cover\"/> <div class=\"right\"> <h4 class=\"name\"> <a href=\"/book/620a32b99aad6e54aaa27b1d\" target=\"_blank\">九星霸体诀（又名：玄天霸体录）</a> </h4> <p class=\"author\"> <span>平凡魔术师</span> <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"cat\">玄幻</span> </p> <p class=\"desc\">是丹帝重生？是融合灵魂？被盗走灵根、灵血、灵骨的三无少年——龙尘，凭借着记忆中的炼丹神术，修行神秘功法九星霸体诀，拨开重重迷雾，解开惊天之局。\r\n手掌天地乾坤，脚踏日月星辰，镇压恶鬼邪神。\r\n江湖传闻：龙尘一到，地吼天啸。龙尘一出，鬼泣神哭。</p> <p class=\"popularity\">  <span class=\"c-red\">4.94万</span>人气  <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"c-red\">86.41%</span>读者留存 </p> </div> <a href=\"/book/620a32b99aad6e54aaa27b1d/1.html\" class=\"btn-read\" target=\"_blank\">开始阅读</a> </div>  <div data-href=\"/book/53fe5d22dae2138d411e66a3\" class=\"book\"> <img src=\"http://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/agent/http%3A%2F%2Fimg.1391.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fbookcenter%2Fcover%2F1%2F164083%2F164083_9c351f543ab0453db54cac29b85a1d13.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=\"https://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/img-bk.png\"' alt=\"仙破苍穹\" class=\"cover\"/> <div class=\"right\"> <h4 class=\"name\"> <a href=\"/book/53fe5d22dae2138d411e66a3\" target=\"_blank\">仙破苍穹</a> </h4> <p class=\"author\"> <span>不怕输的人</span> <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"cat\">仙侠</span> </p> <p class=\"desc\">在这个以武道为主的大陆上,经过了数百万年的沧桑历史,终于迎来了一个大时代,法宝,秘籍如泉喷涌,造就了无数的天才.  而在这杀性凛冽的漫漫白骨路上,我要将敌人给我的痛苦化作我的力量,君破苍穹!</p> <p class=\"popularity\">  <span class=\"c-red\">2.24万</span>人气  <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"c-red\">50.84%</span>读者留存 </p> </div> <a href=\"/book/53fe5d22dae2138d411e66a3/1.html\" class=\"btn-read\" target=\"_blank\">开始阅读</a> </div>  <div data-href=\"/book/5c2c8844e820cd1bde357d51\" class=\"book\"> <img src=\"http://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/agent/http%3A%2F%2Fimg.1391.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fbookcenter%2Fcover%2F1%2F3344208%2F3344208_677cbd2191414b22a35da168245ff92f.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=\"https://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/img-bk.png\"' alt=\"邪王专宠：绝世狂妃破苍穹\" class=\"cover\"/> <div class=\"right\"> <h4 class=\"name\"> <a href=\"/book/5c2c8844e820cd1bde357d51\" target=\"_blank\">邪王专宠：绝世狂妃破苍穹</a> </h4> <p class=\"author\"> <span>鸢尾笑</span> <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"cat\">幻想言情</span> </p> <p class=\"desc\">一朝睁眼，横行黑道的首席佣兵成了废材庶女！爹不疼没娘爱，不能修炼，连十三岁的小屁孩也敢骑在她头上？半日洗髓，堪比常人十年苦练！圣兽丹药信手拈来，若她是废材，敢问世人为何物？哼，神器在手看她如何打怪炼丹虐白莲！韬光养晦十六年，风华展露破苍穹。待到风起云涌时，他握紧了她的手：“若你豪情疏狂，我便陪你征战天下，傲世苍穹。”</p> <p class=\"popularity\">  <span class=\"c-red\">2.23万</span>人气  <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"c-red\">54.3%</span>读者留存 </p> </div> <a href=\"/book/5c2c8844e820cd1bde357d51/1.html\" class=\"btn-read\" target=\"_blank\">开始阅读</a> </div>  <div data-href=\"/book/582c5a538749a5bb5d032d97\" class=\"book\"> <img src=\"http://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/agent/http%3A%2F%2Fimg.1391.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fbookcenter%2Fcover%2F1%2F1529426%2F_1529426_024607.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=\"https://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/img-bk.png\"' alt=\"我的老公帅破苍穹\" class=\"cover\"/> <div class=\"right\"> <h4 class=\"name\"> <a href=\"/book/582c5a538749a5bb5d032d97\" target=\"_blank\">我的老公帅破苍穹</a> </h4> <p class=\"author\"> <span>云谁之思</span> <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"cat\">科幻空间</span> </p> <p class=\"desc\">一觉睡了一千年来到未来不算什么稀奇事，莫名其妙有了老公成了弃妇也不算稀奇事，而当有人将四盆盆栽放在尤槿面前，说是她儿子的时候，这就是稀奇事了。星历691年某日的清晨，一条新闻席卷整个星盟——英俊多金的星盟少将傅承至今未娶的原因竟是男言之隐……顶着大肚子、抱着一捧娃的尤槿：“新闻果然是骗人的！”</p> <p class=\"popularity\">  <span class=\"c-red\">2.23万</span>人气  <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"c-red\">58.4%</span>读者留存 </p> </div> <a href=\"/book/582c5a538749a5bb5d032d97/1.html\" class=\"btn-read\" target=\"_blank\">开始阅读</a> </div>  <div data-href=\"/book/5c765103d15a172f35fe9df1\" class=\"book\"> <img src=\"http://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/agent/http%3A%2F%2Fimg.1391.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fbookcenter%2Fcover%2F1%2F3337001%2F3337001_898efe1695a84332ba1d6eed74359649.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=