610690_50b6120ea86f4f4c91d6f0e73cfcdde9.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=\"https://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/img-bk.png\"' alt=\"斗破苍穹之药族崛起\" class=\"cover\"/> <div class=\"right\"> <h4 class=\"name\"> <a href=\"/book/6204d1fcd728f6817f4ab2ff\" target=\"_blank\">斗破苍穹之药族崛起</a> </h4> <p class=\"author\"> <span>豫记大烩菜</span> <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"cat\">轻小说</span> </p> <p class=\"desc\">穿越斗破十年，药灵胎刚得到金手指，啪叽一下，老爹死了。\n好在，有药帝老祖宗留下的机缘，他才不至于饿死在街头。\n大千世界，太古神诀，借助神木灵药之力，夺天造化塑神脉！\n一药一灵脉，一脉一神通，看药灵胎如何凭借神诀之力，凝聚无上九神脉！\n探究神秘焚诀起源，寻求失落的原始法身，斗气大陆是否存在海洋，远古的诸帝飞升又是为何？\n一切的一切，都在本书中！</p> <p class=\"popularity\">  <span class=\"c-red\">2.15万</span>人气  <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"c-red\">50.47%</span>读者留存 </p> </div> <a href=\"/book/6204d1fcd728f6817f4ab2ff/1.html\" class=\"btn-read\" target=\"_blank\">开始阅读</a> </div>  <div data-href=\"/book/60225f8560a9c604491be471\" class=\"book\"> <img src=\"http://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/agent/http%3A%2F%2Fimg.1391.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fbookcenter%2Fcover%2F1%2F3527019%2F3527019_9106802e0a1d4ff0afd3176bb06c4b0a.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=\"https://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/img-bk.png\"' alt=\"刀破苍穹.\" class=\"cover\"/> <div class=\"right\"> <h4 class=\"name\"> <a href=\"/book/60225f8560a9c604491be471\" target=\"_blank\">刀破苍穹.</a> </h4> <p class=\"author\"> <span>何无恨</span> <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"cat\">玄幻</span> </p> <p class=\"desc\">诛邪魔，斗天神，挥刀破苍穹！\n  现代宅男穿越异界，成为玉京城头号大纨绔，一个废物大少爷。\n  幸好他拥有刀魂升级系统，杀妖兽、杀人都能升级变强，而且修炼没有瓶颈，更能获得神级功法，神通绝学。\n  昔日的废物大少爷终于逆袭，踩绝顶天才，灭至尊强者，铸就一段华丽的武神传说！\n  嚣张彪悍的人生，从此开始！</p> <p class=\"popularity\">  <span class=\"c-red\">2.14万</span>人气  <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"c-red\">51.49%</span>读者留存 </p> </div> <a href=\"/book/60225f8560a9c604491be471/1.html\" class=\"btn-read\" target=\"_blank\">开始阅读</a> </div>  <div data-href=\"/book/53815dfebbd00c030903b674\" class=\"book\"> <img src=\"http://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/agent/http%3A%2F%2Fimg.1391.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fbookcenter%2Fcover%2F1%2F1181411%2F_1181411_590197.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=\"https://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/img-bk.png\"' alt=\"气破苍穹\" class=\"cover\"/> <div class=\"right\"> <h4 class=\"name\"> <a href=\"/book/53815dfebbd00c030903b674\" target=\"_blank\">气破苍穹</a> </h4> <p class=\"author\"> <span>于小少</span> <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"cat\">玄幻</span> </p> <p class=\"desc\">“灵武大陆强者为尊!天才昊焱父母神秘离奇双亡! 而后少年更是背负废材之名，倍受欺凌，是他人所为，还是天欲欺他？ 获神秘玉佩，他洗筋伐髓再度修炼! 以雷霆之资震慑众人，更以鲲鹏之躯逆天伐仙! 修武技、收异兽、斗宗族。 步步为营，险象环生…… 且看少年昊焱如何气破苍穹成为不世传奇！ “</p> <p class=\"popularity\">  <span class=\"c-red\">2.13万</span>人气  <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"c-red\">47.38%</span>读者留存 </p> </div> <a href=\"/book/53815dfebbd00c030903b674/1.html\" class=\"btn-read\" target=\"_blank\">开始阅读</a> </div>  <div data-href=\"/book/5bced108af630f0dda0b07c1\" class=\"book\"> <img src=\"http://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/agent/http%3A%2F%2Fimg.1391.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fbookcenter%2Fcover%2F1%2F3322144%2F3322144_d090d5e992fa4bd69cf44b4ccab05a3f.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=\"https://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/img-bk.png\"' alt=\"王者荣耀之剑破苍穹\" class=\"cover\"/> <div class=\"right\"> <h4 class=\"name\"> <a href=\"/book/5bced108af630f0dda0b07c1\" target=\"_blank\">王者荣耀之剑破苍穹</a> </h4> <p class=\"author\"> <span>风凌宇</span> <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"cat\">玄幻</span> </p> <p class=\"desc\">相传，在宇宙毁灭又重生的另一个时空中，有一块神奇的大陆，它拥有着不同寻常的力量。无数英雄超越时间、超越空间、超越一切法则，重生在这里。\n    在这块大陆上，他们拥有了神奇的力量。以不同的信仰，不同的精神和不同的文化底蕴，续写着新的传奇。\n    而这块大陆，人们称之为“王者大陆”。</p> <p class=\"popularity\">  <span class=\"c-red\">2.12万</span>人气  <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"c-red\">47.52%</span>读者留存 </p> </div> <a href=\"/book/5bced108af630f0dda0b07c1/1.html\" class=\"btn-read\" target=\"_blank\">开始阅读</a> </div>  <div data-href=\"/book/54cc4337dbf3d2603f8d8552\" class=\"book\"> <img src=\"http://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/agent/http%3A%2F%2Fimg.1391.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fbookcenter%2Fcover%2F1%2F357456%2F_357456_357782.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=\"https://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/img-bk.png\"' alt=\"网游之刺破苍穹\" class=\"cover\"/> <div class=\"right\"> <h4 class=\"name\"> <a href=\"/book/54cc4337dbf3d2603f8d8552\" target=\"_blank\">网游之刺破苍穹</a> </h4> <p class=\"author\"> <span>七分醉</span> <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"cat\">游戏</span> </p> <p class=\"desc\">杜羽为生活所迫进入游戏,在小人的逼迫下重燃斗志,以自创的轮回战技不断击败对手,一步步踏上金字塔的巅峰,成为游戏内外的无冕之王!  隐藏职业必须有,刺破天!  俊男美女必须多,叼炸天!  无耻人渣必须踩,艹翻天!  ——好书需养分,望支持!</p> <p class=\"popularity\">  <span class=\"c-red\">2.11万</span>人气  <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"c-red\">41.26%</span>读者留存 </p> </div> <a href=\"/book/54cc4337dbf3d2603f8d8552/1.html\" class=\"btn-read\" target=\"_blank\">开始阅读</a> </div>  <div data-href=\"/book/663c44fddc101915283e3b44\" class=\"book\"> <img src=\"http://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/agent/http%3A%2F%2Fimg.1391.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fbookcenter%2Fcover%2F1%2F3647184%2F3647184_675688462dc841ce925106e312436841.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=\"https://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/img-bk.png\"' alt=\"一剑破苍穹\" class=\"cover\"/> <div class=\"right\"> <h4 class=\"name\"> <a href=\"/book/663c44fddc101915283e3b44\" target=\"_blank\">一剑破苍穹</a> </h4> <p class=\"author\"> <span>尺短情长</span> <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"cat\">玄幻</span> </p> <p class=\"desc\">一场血肉铸就的登神之路延展开来，普通大学生苏恒穿越异世，为了活下去，他必须不断修行，一剑破天，一剑斩魔，且看他如何逆天而行！</p> <p class=\"popularity\">  <span class=\"c-red\">2.10万</span>人气  <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"c-red\">47.77%</span>读者留存 </p> </div> <a href=\"/book/663c44fddc101915283e3b44/1.html\" class=\"btn-read\" target=\"_blank\">开始阅读</a> </div>  <div data-href=\"/book/5f8e4f8157f52884cdfb291e\" class=\"book\"> <img src=\"http://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/agent/http%3A%2F%2Fimg.1391.com%2Fapi%2Fv1%2Fbookcenter%2Fcover%2F1%2F3449883%2F3449883_897ad3f57fe4483ca34f49868f5160db.jpg%2F?imageMogr2/thumbnail/180x200\" onerror='this.src=\"https://statics.zhuishushenqi.com/img-bk.png\"' alt=\"撞灵就变强\" class=\"cover\"/> <div class=\"right\"> <h4 class=\"name\"> <a href=\"/book/5f8e4f8157f52884cdfb291e\" target=\"_blank\">撞灵就变强</a> </h4> <p class=\"author\"> <span>欲破苍穹九万里</span> <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"cat\">都市</span> </p> <p class=\"desc\">一个年轻人李阳意外获得一个神秘撞灵系统，自此开始了不一样的人生，\n午夜来临几只小鬼聚在一起说：“最近有个叫李阳的总是扮猪吃老虎的，遇见他躲着点走!”\n“啊嚏，谁在说我呢！”\n李阳走在夜晚的小道上悠哉的晃着小步子……</p> <p class=\"popularity\">  <span class=\"c-red\">2.10万</span>人气  <span class=\"split\">|</span> <span class=\"c-red\">47.13%</span>读者留存 </p> </div> <a href=\"/book/5f8e4f8157f52884cdfb291e/1.html\" class=\"btn-read\" target=\"_blank\">开始阅读</a> </div>  </div> <div class=\"c-full-page\"> <span class=\"total\">共<span class=\"c-gold\">2</span>页</span> <a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"prev\">上一页</a> <ul class=\"pageNumber\">  <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"/search?val=%E6%96%97%E7%A0%B4%E8%8B%8D%E7%A9%B9&amp;page=1\">1</a></li>  <li class=\"\"><a href=\"/search?val=%E6%96%97%E7%A0%B4%E8%8B%8D%E7%A9%B9&amp;page=2\">2</a></li>  </ul> <a href=\"/search?val=%E6%96%97%E7%A0%B4%E8%8B%8D%E7%A9%B9&amp;page=2\" class=\"next\">下一页</a> <div class=\"jump\"> <span>跳转到</span> <input id=\"page-input\" class=\"page-input\" type=\"text\" name=\"pageNumber\" value=\"\"> <button id=\"page-go\" class=\"page-go\" type=\"button\" data-link=\"/search?val=%E6%96%97%E7%A0%B4%E8%8B%8D%E7%A9%B9&amp;page=\" data-total=\"2\">GO</button> </div> </div>  </div> </section> <footer class=\"c-full-footer\"> <div class=\"container\"> <div class=\"clearfix foot\"> <div class=\"footer-left\"> <div class=\"info\"> <a href=\"/download\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">客户端</a> <span>|</span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"/about?type=aboutUs\">关于我们</a> <span>|</span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"/about?type=news\">新闻动态</a> <span>|</span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"/about?type=callUs\">联系我们</a> <span>|</span> <a rel=\"nofo